co.paralleluniverse.galaxy.cluster

Class DistributedTree.ListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.paralleluniverse.galaxy.cluster.DistributedTree.ListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DistributedTree.Listener
    Enclosing interface:
    DistributedTree

    public abstract static class DistributedTree.ListenerAdapter
extends Object
implements DistributedTree.Listener
    An abstract adapter class for receiving DistributedTree events. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating listener objects.
